Sets Traktor's 'BPM Lock On' to ‘off’, calls Traktor's 'BPM x2' (double the BPM/tempo of the track).
Shifted: Sets Traktor's 'BPM Lock On' to ‘off’, calls Traktor's 'BPM /2' (halve the BPM/tempo of the track).

Calls Traktor's 'Duplicate Track Deck B’ (copy source of Deck B to Deck A)

Purpose: Sets/Displays Traktor's 'Freeze Mode On' (toggle freeze mode on and off, easier than using the S8 as Supreme Mod makes Freeze a shifted function)
Sets/Displays Traktor's 'Freeze Slice Count Adjust' (required to achieve 16 slices, as it defaults to 8 slices after freeze is engaged)

Sets Traktor's 'Play/Pause (Deck Common)’ to 0 (‘Pause’) (stop playback of the focussed deck - use after exiting freeze mode)

Calls Live's 'Phase Nudge Up' button via M4L device 'CT6 Params’ (nudge Live's audio output into time with Traktor's by increasing Live's tempo for as long as the button is held down. The M4L device facilitates mapping the CCs to Live's API the LOM to avoid having to MIDI map these controls on a per-set basis)

Purpose:
